    <!-- ══ 09 · USAGE GUIDELINES ═════════════════════ -->
    <div class="sg-section">
      <div class="sg-section__header">
        <span class="sg-section__num">09</span>
        <h2 class="sg-section__heading">Usage Guidelines</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="sg-guidelines-grid">
        <div class="sg-rule sg-rule--do">
          <p class="sg-rule__verdict">✓ Do</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Use Magenta for primary CTAs, active states, and brand moments — buttons, underlines, key typographic highlights.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Use Warm Beige and White for the majority of surface area.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Use Purple exclusively for the AMK badge and informational UI states.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Use Sepia for muted meta text and earthy illustration accents.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Apply the dark overlay (55% opacity) on hero images for text legibility.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Write headlines in Title Case using Poppins Bold.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Write body copy in Sentence case using DM Sans Regular.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Write eyebrow labels in ALL CAPS, DM Sans Medium, wide letter-spacing.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Reserve italic only for the brand tagline — "Truly! Softly!"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sg-rule sg-rule--dont">
          <p class="sg-rule__verdict">✗ Don't</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Never use Magenta as a large background — it overwhelms. Keep it as an accent.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Never hardcode hex values in component CSS — always consume CSS tokens from base.css.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Don't use Purple for general decorative purposes — it's reserved for the AMK badge.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Don't use cold grey shadows — all shadows must be warm-toned (magenta or near-black).</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Don't mix Poppins and DM Sans for the same typographic role in a single component.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Don't use --radius-full on structural layout elements — only badges and tags.</p>
          <p class="sg-rule__text">Don't use italic on anything other than the brand tagline.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

